divs: Sighting Detailsmy girl friend and i seen this cross like object just hovering to our left we pulled the motorcycle over and watched it for like a min i just wrote it off as a heli but like 1 and half hour later we were heading home and seen the object not in the same place but a few miles away still dont know what it was
